600
01:02:21,660 --> 01:02:23,628
N-Newt.

601
01:02:25,620 --> 01:02:29,147
- What'd you say? - Newt.

602
01:02:29,220 --> 01:02:31,427
My name's Newt.

603
01:02:31,500 --> 01:02:36,631
Nobody calls me Rebecca except my brother.

604
01:02:36,740 --> 01:02:40,586
Newt? I like that.

605
01:02:40,700 --> 01:02:44,466
I'm Ripley. It's nice to meet you.

606
01:02:46,500 --> 01:02:49,583
And who is this, hmm?

607
01:02:49,700 --> 01:02:53,421
- Casey. - Hello, Casey.

608
01:02:53,500 --> 01:02:56,470
What about your brother? What's his name?

609
01:02:56,540 --> 01:02:58,588
Timmy.

610
01:02:58,660 --> 01:03:03,143
Is Timmy around here too? Maybe hiding like you were?

611
01:03:06,180 --> 01:03:08,148
Any sisters?

612
01:03:11,740 --> 01:03:13,663
Mom and dad?

613
01:03:16,500 --> 01:03:20,789
Newt, look at me. Where are they?

614
01:03:20,860 --> 01:03:23,909
They're dead, all right? Can I go now?

615
01:03:27,020 --> 01:03:29,500
I'm sorry, Newt.

616
01:03:29,580 --> 01:03:32,151
Don't you think you'd be safer here with us?

617
01:03:36,020 --> 01:03:38,068
